race.description: Cup Packages Selling Fast Through Trybooking Mdn
race.comment: STATEWIDE (8) resumes and just missed in the Group 3 WA Sires Produce Stakes at Ascot over 1400m when last seen. He'd shown plenty leading into that and has been gelded. Went close in a recent Belmont trial and is the testing material.  LA EXCELLENCE (3) resumes off two narrow defeats at this track and has a Belmont trial warmer. He can be in the finish in this lineup. won't be too far away.  NO SHORT MAN (7) debuts and has had five trials stretching back to last year. Has shown ability and is likely to race well. TRAILER TRUCK (9) has also been well-trialled for his debut and placed the latest at Belmont. He is worth a look at a price.
